<dl id="n40032b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40032b">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40032b"> 32(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> cheris</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Many of <font color="green">[the outcastes&apos;]</font> hamlets (called <i>cheris</i> in South India) are a huddle of huts in a confined space, filthy to the last degree and surrounded by filth. <small> Rev W.S. Hunt, <a name="WSHI1" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#WSHI1"><cite title="source">India's Outcastes: A New Era</cite></a> (1924) 36</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
